        <updateDate>2013-05-16T22:19:26Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Requires the Secretary of Commerce, beginning with the 2020 decennial census, to attribute an individual who is incarcerated in a state, federal, county, or municipal correctional center as of the date on which such census is taken to such individual's last place of residence before incarceration. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
